{"tid":674762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「女人街」鹹淡水管齊爆路陷　近百排檔停業","createTime":"2018-05-23T03:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T03:54:49.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f56f86f33b69751b8a4699762f117444ffbdf9e0","tid":674762,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/photo/bkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180523105339\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180523105339&h=4661416d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">爆水管現場路陷現大窿。(吳建明攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n旺角爆鹹水及淡水管封路，凌晨4時許，俗稱「女人街」的通菜街近2號對出馬路，地底一條直徑約15吋的鹹水管，以及一條直徑約6吋的淡水管突然爆裂，路面下陷形成一個面積約2米乘3米的大窿，深越1米，大量鹹、淡水湧出馬路，幸當時商舖均已關門，未有造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n水務署派職員到場搶修，附近一帶鹹水供應受影響，而食水供應則不受影響。運輸署今晨6時21分宣布，因通菜街介乎豉油街與登打士街之間的全線現已封閉，交通受阻。受路陷影響，女人街近100個排檔未能開檔，檔主叫苦，有居民則忙於清理淤泥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/photo/bkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001_03b.jpg?20180523105339\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20180523105339&h=73bed8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">馬路滿布黃泥水。(吳建明攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/bkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fbkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001.html&d=9hIK144lkxzBKkv7H8CMvTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3348d5f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/bkn-20180523063555067-0523_00822_001.html</a>"}]}